    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·鲁宾（Robert Rubin</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/robert-rubin-says-us-fiscal-trajectory-is-enormously-dangerous</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前财政部长罗伯特·鲁宾（Robert Rubin）表示，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的经济政策在他六个十年的职业生涯中引起了“最大的不确定性”，警告说，他们将破坏信心，使美国财政轨迹和危害全球舞台上的美国信誉危害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/robert-rubin-says-us-fiscal-trajectory-is-enormously-dangerous</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 16:27:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街想知道何时特朗普何时随着股票不断下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/wall-street-wonders-when-trump-steps-in-as-stocks-keep-falling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的贸易政策，粘性通货膨胀和突然脆弱的经济受到威胁，但由于股票在上个月弹跳高高时，战略家认为一只无形的手正在起作用：特朗普的手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/wall-street-wonders-when-trump-steps-in-as-stocks-keep-falling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 15:49:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战争的贸易战争市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/us-yield-curve-steepens-on-growth-angst-with-tariffs-now-reality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贸易商正在押注，即美联储将在唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税上加息可能会降低利率，威胁到已经削弱的美国经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/us-yield-curve-steepens-on-growth-angst-with-tariffs-now-reality</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 10:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普升级了全球贸易战，引发了卖山雀的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统施加了他对加拿大和墨西哥的威胁，并以全面的进口征税征收，并对中国的现有指控增加了一倍，这激发了迅速报复，这使世界经济陷入了深入的贸易战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布伦特石油在贸易战中降至70美元以下，欧佩克+生产加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自10月以来，全球基准Brent原油首次下跌每桶70美元以下，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税开始了一系列贸易战，欧佩克+搬运了多年来停止的生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 23:29:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
